however,
official transcripts will be required at the time of hire), three
letters of
recommendation, and statement of teaching philosophy electronically to
gersting@hawaii.edu or by mail to Dr. Judith Gersting, Chair, Computer
Science
Department, University of Hawaii at Hilo, 200 W. Kawili Street, Hilo, HI
96720-4091.

